OL,6,FA British Airways captain who
OL,7,Fbludgeoned his wife to death more than
OL,8,F13 years ago will not be freed from
OL,9,Fprison.
OL,11,FRobert Brown bludgeoned 46-year-old
OL,12,FJoanna Simpson with a claw hammer in
OL,13,Ftheir family home in Berkshire in
OL,14,FOctober 2010, as their two young
OL,15,Fchildren cowered in a playroom.
OL,17,FThe killing was the subject of a
OL,18,Frecent two-part ITV documentary The
OL,19,FBritish Airways Killer.
