OL,6,FBrown's High Court challenge against a
OL,7,Fgovernment move to block his automatic
OL,8,Frelease from prison was dismissed by
OL,9,FMr Justice Ritchie on Wednesday.
OL,11,FBrown, who was jailed for 26 years in
OL,12,F2011, claimed that "political
OL,13,Fmotivation" amid a media campaign
OL,14,Fagainst his release improperly
OL,15,Fcontributed to a decision to refer his
OL,16,Fcase to the Parole Board.
OL,18,FHis lawyers argued at a hearing in
OL,19,FLondon earlier this month that Justice
OL,20,FSecretary Alex Chalk's referral was
OL,21,Funlawful.
