OL,6,FHe was due to be automatically freed
OL,7,Fon licence halfway through his
OL,8,Fsentence in November last year, but Ms
OL,9,FSimpson's friends and family urged Mr
OL,10,FChalk to intervene.
OL,12,FIn October 2023, the minister used new
OL,13,Fpowers to have Brown's case reviewed
OL,14,Fby the Parole Board, an independent
OL,15,Fbody that carries out risk assessments
OL,16,Fon prisoners to determine whether they
OL,17,Fcan be safely released.
