OL,6,FHis legal team said the risk posed by
OL,7,FBrown had not increased and that he
OL,8,Fhad been "subjected to a high-profile
OL,9,Fcampaign through the media and with
OL,10,Fpoliticians that has sought to block
OL,11,Fhis release".
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Justice (MOJ) rejected
OL,14,Fhis allegations, arguing that Mr Chalk
OL,15,F"in no way seeks to 'go behind' or
OL,16,F'disapply' or 'fail to respect' the
OL,17,Fsentencing court's decision".
